data.description: Extensively remodeled 3BR/2BA condominium in the heart of West Knoxville.  Complete with high-end finishes and additions throughout. Hardwood flooring. Granite countertops. New kitchen and bath cabinetry through out. Tile bathrooms , showers  and floors. Spacious bedrooms with extra large closets. Many extra storage areas including custom storage pantry and closet at entry. Screened porch. Ventless washer and dryer area. Large, open living room dining area. Concrete construction insulates unit, lowers utility bills and reduces sound.  New windows already purchased and scheduled for install in mid-October. So many features, it is impossible to mention all of them here. THIS PROPERTY IS A MUST SEE TO BELIEVE!
